Detailed Description

Label managed object.

Verify that no two labels have the same name by posting notifications upon name change.

[implementation]

Controls special cases of key-value changes.

Prevents the name change of immutable labels (e.g. "no-label" label). Posts a ZXLabelNameDidChangeNotification after label name is changed.
